select语句，区间比较的查询条件  exists ,all, any
不会裁剪  含有子查询的表达式不会用于分区裁剪
select id,date_col from lyq_test where exists (select id,date_col from lyq_test where date_col > '2023-02-01') limit 5;
+----+------------+
| id | date_col   |
+----+------------+
|  1 | 2023-01-01 |
|  5 | 2023-01-02 |
|  2 | 2023-02-01 |
|  3 | 2023-03-01 |
|  4 | 2023-04-01 |
+----+------------+
